#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:16
msgid "Nice And Easy Does It All the Time"
msgstr "Air do shocair"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:18
msgid ""
"I am sorry, but will I have to tear this down again. We might need the space"
" here later on. If I am too slow for you, you might want to play a real game"
" and just find everything out for yourself. Otherwise, please bear with me, "
"I am not the youngest and quickest anymore."
msgstr "Tha mi duilich, ach feumaidh mi seo a mhilleadh a-rithist. Dh’fhaoidte gum bi sinn feumach air an rum fhathast. Ma tha mi ro shlaodach dhut, ’s dòcha gum b’ fhearr leat fìor gheama a chluiche agus a h-uile rud ionnsachadh leat fhèin. Mura b’ fhearr, air do shocair o chionn ’s nach eil mi cho òg ’s luath mar a bha."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:26
msgid "Welcome to the Widelands Tutorial!"
msgstr "Fàilte dhan oideachadh aig Widelands!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:28
msgid "Welcome to Widelands!"
msgstr "Fàilte do Widelands!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:29
msgid ""
"Widelands is a slow-paced build-up strategy game with an emphasis on "
"construction rather than destruction. This tutorial will guide you through "
"the basics of the game."
msgstr "’S e geama ro-innleachd mhall a th’ ann am Widelands le cuideam air togail seach milleadh. Seallaidh an t-oideachadh seo dhut na tha bunasach sa gheama."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:31
msgid "Dismiss this box by left-clicking on the button below."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut am bogsa seo a leigeil seachad le briogadh clì air a’ phutan gu h-ìosal."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:37
msgid "Diving In"
msgstr "A’ tòiseachadh"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:41
msgid "Let’s dive right in!"
msgstr "Nach tòisich sinn sa bhad!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:42
msgid ""
"There are three different tribes in Widelands: the Barbarians, the Empire "
"and the Atlanteans. All tribes have a different economy, strength and "
"weaknesses, but the general gameplay is the same for all. We will play the "
"Barbarians for now."
msgstr "Tha trì treubhan diofraichte ann am Widelands: na Tùsanaich, an Impireachd is na h-Atlantaich. Tha eaconamaidh, neartan is laigsean eadar-dhealaichte aig gach treubh, ach cluichidh tu an geama san aon dòigh le gach tè dhiubh. Bidh sinn ’nar Tùsanaich an-dràsta."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:43
msgid ""
"You will usually start the game with one headquarters. This is the big "
"building with the blue flag in front of it. The headquarters is a warehouse "
"that stores wares, workers and soldiers. Some wares are needed for building "
"houses, others for making other wares. Obviously, the wares in the "
"headquarters will not last forever, so you must make sure to replace them. "
"The most important wares in the early game are the basic construction wares:"
" logs and raw stone. Let’s make sure that we do not run out of logs. For "
"this, we need a lumberjack and a hut for him to stay in."
msgstr "Tòisichidh tu air geama le aon phrìomh-àras mar as trice. Seo an togalach mòr leis a’ bhratach ghorm air a bheulaibh. ’S e taigh-stòrais a ghlèidheas bathair, obraichean is saighdearan a tha sa phrìomh-àras. Bidh feum air cuid a bhathar gus taighean a thogail is air cuid eile gus bathar eile a dhèanamh. Gu follaiseach, cha mhair am bathar sa phrìomh-àras gu bràth is feumaidh tu dèanamh cinnteach gun dèan thu barrachd dheth. Is fiodh agus clachan am bathar togail bunasach as cudromaiche aig toiseach a’ gheama. Dèanamaid cinnteach nach ruith am fiodh oirnn. Bidh feum againn air coilltear agus air bothan sa ghabhas e còmhnaidh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:44
msgid ""
"We need to find a nice place for the lumberjack’s hut. To make this easier, "
"we can activate ‘Show Building Spaces’. There are two ways you can do this, "
"either by clicking on the ‘Show Building Spaces’ button at the bottom of the"
" screen, which is the fourth one from the left. Or you can use the SPACE key"
" to toggle it."
msgstr "Feumaidh sinn àite ghoireasach a lorg airson bothan a’ choillteir. Nochdamaid na h-ionadan togail gus seo a dhèanamh nas fhasa. Tha dà dhòigh ann gus am feart seo a chur air. Air an dàrna dòigh, briog air a’ phutan “Nochd ionadan togail (air/dheth)” aig bonn na sgrìn, seo an ceathramh putan on taobh chlì. Air an dòigh eile, brùth air an iuchair SPACE gus a thoglachadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:46
msgid "Left-click the ‘OK’ button to close this box and then try it."
msgstr "Dèan briogadh clì air a’ phutan “Ceart ma-thà” gus am bogsa seo a dhùnadh is feuch e an uairsin."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:49
msgid "Enable the showing of building spaces"
msgstr "Nochd na h-ionadan togail"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:51
msgid "Show Building Spaces"
msgstr "Nochd na h-ionadan togail"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:52
msgid ""
"It is easier to understand what type of buildings can be built on which "
"field when the symbols for the building spaces are enabled."
msgstr "Tha e nas fhasa tuigsinn na dh’fhaodas tu togail air gach raon ma bhios samhlaidhean nan ionadan togail an comas."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:54
msgid ""
"Do so now, either by pressing SPACE or by clicking the fourth button from "
"the left at the very bottom of the screen. Right-click on this window and "
"then give it a try."
msgstr "Dèan seo a-nis is brùth air SPACE no briog air a’ cheathramh putan on taobh chlì aig bonn na sgrìn. Dèan briogadh deas air an uinneag seo is feuch e."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:59
msgid "Lumberjack’s Spot"
msgstr "Àite airson bothan coillteir"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:63
msgid ""
"There you go. I will explain about all those symbols in a minute. First, let"
" me show you how to make a lumberjack’s hut and how to connect it with a "
"road. There is a sweet spot for a lumberjack right next to those trees. I’ll"
" describe the steps I will take and then ask you to click on the ‘OK’ button"
" for me to demonstrate."
msgstr "Sin thu fhèin! Mìnichidh mi mu na samhlaidhean seo uile a dh’aithghearr. An toiseach, seallaidh mi dhut mar a thogas tu bothan coillteir is mar a cheanglas tu ri rathad e. Tha deagh àite airson coillteir ri taobh nan craobhan ud. Mìnichidh mi na ceuman a ghabhas mi is an uairsin iarraidh mi ort gum briog thu air a’ phutan “Ceart ma-thà” ach an seall mi seo dhut."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:70
msgid "Building the Lumberjack"
msgstr "A’ togail bothan coillteir"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:73
msgid ""
"First, I’ll left-click on the symbol where I want the lumberjack’s hut to be"
" built. A window will appear where I can choose between buildings. Because "
"I’ll click a yellow house symbol – which means that its field can house "
"medium and small buildings – I am presented with all the medium buildings "
"that I can build. The lumberjack’s hut is a small building, so I will go on "
"to select the small buildings tab. Then I’ll choose the lumberjack’s hut."
msgstr "An toiseach, nì mi briogadh clì air an t-samhla far a bheil mi airson am bothan coillteir a thogail. Nochdaidh uinneag far an urrainn dhomh togalach a thaghadh. On a nì mi briogadh air samhla buidhe – is ciall dha seo gu bheil rum san raon airson togalaich mheadhanaich no bhig – chì mi na h-uile togalach meadhanach a b’ urrainn dhomh togail. ’S e togalach beag a th’ anns a’ bhothan choillteir is mar sin taghaidh mi taba nan togalaichean beaga. Taghaidh mi am bothan coillteir an uairsin."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:75
msgid ""
"Click the ‘OK’ button to watch me. I’ll go really slowly: I will click – "
"then select the tab – and finally I’ll choose the building."
msgstr "Briog air a’ phutan “Ceart ma-thà” gus coimhead orm. Nì mi gu fìor shlaodach e. Briogaidh mi – taghaidh mi an taba an uairsin – is taghaidh mi an togalach aig an deireadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:81
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:92
msgid "Building a Connecting Road"
msgstr "A’ togail rathad a cheanglas"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:84
msgid ""
"That won’t do yet. I still need to connect the lumberjack’s hut to the rest "
"of my road network. After ordering the construction site, I was "
"automatically put into road building mode, so all I have to do is click on "
"the blue flag in front of my headquarters."
msgstr "Cha dèan seo a’ chùis fhathast. Feumaidh mi am bothan coillteir a cheangal ris a’ chorr dhe na rathaidean agam. Nuair a bha mi air an làrach-togail òrdachadh, chaidh mo chur ann am modh togail rathaidean gu fèin-obrachail, mar sin cha leig mi leas ach briogadh air a’ bhratach ghorm air beulaibh a’ phrìomh-àrais agam."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:95
msgid ""
"That won’t do yet. I still need to connect the lumberjack’s hut to the rest "
"of my road network. You have disabled the option ‘Start building road after "
"placing a flag’ (to change that, choose ‘Options’ in the Widelands main "
"menu). Therefore, I have entered the road building mode manually. I will "
"tell you later how to do that. To build the road, all I have to do now is "
"click on the blue flag in front of my headquarters."
msgstr "Cha dèan seo a’ chùis fhathast. Feumaidh mi am bothan coillteir a cheangal ris a’ chorr dhe na rathaidean agam fhathast. Chuir thu an roghainn “Tòisich air rathad a thogail às dèidh bratach a thogail” à comas (gus seo atharrachadh, tagh “Roghainnean” ann am prìomh chlàr-taice Widelands). Ma sin, chaidh mi a-steach gun modh togail rathaidean a làimh. Innsidh mi dhut àm eile mar a nì thu seo. Cha leig mi leas ach briogadh air a’ bhratach ghorm air beulaibh a’ phrìomh-àrais agam a-nis gus an rathad a thogail."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:103
msgid "Waiting for the Lumberjack to Go Up"
msgstr "A’ feitheamh gus am bith am bothan coillteir air a thogail"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:106
msgid ""
"Now watch closely while a builder leaves the headquarters and goes to the "
"construction site. Also, a carrier will take position in between the two "
"blue flags and carry wares from one blue flag to the other."
msgstr "Nise, cum sùil air an togalaiche a dh’fhàgas am prìomh-àras is a thèid dhan làrach-togail. Cuideachd, thig giùlanair a sheasamh eadar an dà bhratach ghorm is giùlainidh e bathar on dàrna bhratach ghorm gun tè eile."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:113
msgid "Placing Another Flag"
msgstr "A’ togail bratach eile"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:116
msgid ""
"Nice how they are working, isn’t it? But the poor carrier has a very long "
"way to go. We can make it easier for him (and more efficient for us) by "
"placing another blue flag on the road."
msgstr "Nach math mar a tha iad ag obair? Ach tha slighe fhada ri siubhal aig a’ ghiùlanair bhochd. Nì sinn cùisean nas fhasa dha (is nas èifeachdaiche dhuinne) ma chuireas sinn bratach ghorm eile air an rathad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:118
msgid ""
"You try it this time: click on the yellow flag symbol in between the two "
"blue flags we just placed and then click on the"
msgstr "Feuch thusa ris an turas seo: briog air an t-samhla brataich buidhe eadar an dà bhratach ghorm a tha sinn air a thogail is briog air"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:120
msgid "build flag symbol."
msgstr "an t-samhla “Tog bratach”."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:124
msgid "Build a flag to divide the road to the lumberjack"
msgstr "Roinn an rathad le bratach"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:126
msgid "Build a Flag on the Road"
msgstr "Tog bratach air an rathad"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:127
msgid ""
"The shorter your road segments are, the faster your wares will be "
"transported. You should therefore make sure that your roads have as many "
"flags as possible."
msgstr "Mar as giorra na roinnean-rathaid agad ’s ann nas luaithe a thèid am bathar agad a ghiùlan. Bu chòir dhut dèanamh cinnteach gu bheil an uiread a ghabhas de bhrataich air na rathaidean agad air sàilleibh seo."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:129
msgid ""
"Build a blue flag now in the middle of the road that connects your "
"headquarters to your lumberjack’s hut."
msgstr "Tog bratach ghorm a-nis ann am meadhan an rathaid a cheanglas am prìomh-àras ris a’ bhothan choillteir agad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:134
msgid "Waiting For the Hut to be Finished"
msgstr "A’ feitheamh gus am bith am bothan deiseil"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:137
msgid "Well done! Let’s wait till the hut is finished."
msgstr "Sin thu fhèin! Fuirich ort fhad ’s a thèid am bothan a chrìochnachadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:138
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:151
msgid ""
"If you want things to go faster, simply use the PAGE UP key on your keyboard"
" to increase the game speed. You can use PAGE DOWN to make the game slower "
"again."
msgstr "Ma tha thu airson cùisean a dhèanamh nas luaithe, cha leig thu leas ach an iuchair PAGE UP a chleachdadh air a’ mheur-chlàr agad gus luaths a’ gheama a mheudachadh. Cleachd an iuchair PAGE DOWN gus maille a chur air a’ gheama a-rithist."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:145
msgid "Waiting for the Hut to be Finished"
msgstr "A’ feitheamh gus am bith am bothan deiseil"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:148
msgid ""
"I wanted to teach you how to build new flags, but it seems you have already "
"found out on your own. Well done!"
msgstr "Bha mi airson ionnsachadh dhut mar a thogas tu bratach ùr, ach tha e agad mar-thà a-rèir coltais. Sin thu fhèin!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:149
msgid ""
"Now you have split the road in two parts with a carrier each. This means "
"less work for him and higher efficiency for us. You should therefore always "
"place as many flags as possible on your roads."
msgstr "Tha thu air an rathad a roinneadh ann an dà earrann le giùlanair air gach tè dhiubh. Seo nas lugha de dh’obair dhaibhsan agus barrachd èifeachdachd dhuinne. Mar sin, bu chòir dhut na ghabhas de bhrataichean a chur air na rathaidean agad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:150
msgid "Now we only have to wait till the hut is finished."
msgstr "Cha leig sinn leas ach fuireach a-nis fhad ’s a thèid am bothan a chrìochnachadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:157
msgid "The Construction Site"
msgstr "An làrach-togail"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:159
msgid "Let's see the progress"
msgstr "Thoireamaid sùil air an adhartas"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:160
msgid ""
"If you click on the construction site, a window opens. You can see the wares"
" that are still missing grayed out. You can also see the progress of this "
"construction site."
msgstr "Ma nì thu briogadh air an làrach-togail, nochdaidh uinneag. Chì thu na seòrsaichean bathair a tha a dhìth fhathast le dath liath orra. Chì thu adhartas na làraich-togail cuideachd."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:162
msgid ""
"To close the window, simply right-click on it. All windows in Widelands can "
"be closed that way, except the ones with instructions, like this one. Try it"
" out!"
msgstr "Gus an uinneag a dhùnadh, cha leig thu leas ach briogadh deas a dhèanamh air. Gabhaidh gach uinneag ann an Widelands dùnadh mar seo ach an fheadhainn le stiùireadh annta mar an tè seo fhèin. Siuthad is feuch e!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:169
msgid "Lumberjack is Done"
msgstr "Tha am bothan coillteir deiseil."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:172
msgid ""
"Excellent. The lumberjack’s hut is done. A lumberjack will now move in and "
"start chopping down trees, so our log income is secured for now. Now on to "
"the raw stone."
msgstr "Taghta. Tha am bothan coillteir deiseil. Gabhaidh coilltear còmhnaidh ann a-nis is tòisichidh e air craobhan a leagail. Mar sin, tha teachd a-steach an fhiodha agad cinnteach aig an àm seo. Nise, dhan chlach."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:179
msgid "Some Rocks Were Found"
msgstr "Chaidh creagan a lorg"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:180
msgid "Getting a Quarry Up"
msgstr "A’ togail coireall"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:182
msgid ""
"Stones can be mined in granite mines, but the easier way is to build a "
"quarry next to some rocks lying around. As it happens, there is a pile of "
"them just to the west (left) of your headquarters. I will teach you now how "
"to move your view over there."
msgstr "Gabhaidh clachan a thochladh ann am mèinnean graineil, ach tha e nas fhasa coireall a thogail faisg air creagan air an talamh. Nach goireasach gu bheil tòrr dhiubh dìreach gu siar (gu clì) air a’ phrìomh-àras agad. Innsidh mi dhut mar a ghluaiseas tu an sealladh agad ann."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:184
msgid ""
"There are three ways to move your view. The first one is using the cursor "
"keys on your keyboard. Go ahead and try this out."
msgstr "Tha trì dòighean ann gus an sealladh agad a ghluasad. Is an dàrna dòigh gun chleachd thu na h-iuchraichean saighde air a’ mheur-chlàr agad. Siuthad is feuch e an-dràsta."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:185
msgid "Click the ‘OK’ button and then move the view using the cursor keys"
msgstr "Briog air a’ phutan “Ceart ma-thà” is an uairsin gluais an sealladh leis na h-iuchraichean saighde."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:189
msgid "Move your view with the cursor keys"
msgstr "Gluais an sealladh leis na h-iuchraichean saighde"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:191
msgid "Moving Your View"
msgstr "Gluais an sealladh agad"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:192
msgid ""
"Moving your view is essential to get a complete overview of your whole "
"economy. There are three ways to move your view in Widelands."
msgstr "Tha e riatanach gun gluais thu an sealladh agad ach am faigh thu sealladh slàn air an eaconamaidh agad. Tha trì dòighean ann gus an sealladh agad a ghluasad ann am Widelands."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:194
msgid "The first one is to use the cursor keys on your keyboard."
msgstr "Is gun cleachd thu na h-iuchraichean saighde air a’ mheur-chlàr an dàrna dòigh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:195
msgid ""
"The second one is the more common and faster one: press-and-hold the right "
"mouse button anywhere on the map, then move your mouse around and you’ll see"
" the view scroll."
msgstr "Is an dòigh eile an dòigh as luaithe is as cumanta: briog is cum sìos putan deas na luchaige àite sam bith air a’ mhapa. An uairsin, gluais an luchag agad mu thimcheall is chì thu gun sgrolaich an sealladh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:196
msgid ""
"The third one is to use the minimap. It is especially useful for traveling "
"big distances."
msgstr "Is an treas dòigh am meanbh-mhapa. The e feumail gu h-àraidh gus astar mòr a shiubhal."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:201
msgid "Other Ways to Move the View"
msgstr "Dòighean eile gus an sealladh a ghluasad"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:203
msgid "Excellent. Now there is a faster way to move, using the mouse instead:"
msgstr "Taghta. Nise, tha dòigh as luaithe ann airson gluasad ’s tu a’ cleachdadh na luchaige:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:205
msgid ""
"Simply right-click-and-hold anywhere on the map, then drag the mouse and "
"instead of the cursor, the view will be moved. Try it."
msgstr "Dèan briogadh deas is cum sìos àite sam bith air a’ mhapa is slaod an luchag mu thimcheall. Le sin, gluaisidh an sealladh an àite a’ chùrsair. Feuch e."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:210
msgid "Move your view with the mouse"
msgstr "Gluais an sealladh agad leis an luchag"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:215
msgid "Use the minimap"
msgstr "Cleachdadh a’ mheanbh-mhapa"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:217
msgid ""
"Very good. And now about the minimap. You can open it by clicking on the"
msgstr "Glè mhath. Nise, am mean-mhapa. ‘S urrainn dhut fhosgladh ’s tu a’ briogadh air"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:219
msgid ""
"minimap button at the bottom of the screen or simply by using the keyboard "
"shortcut ‘m’."
msgstr "putan a’ mheanbh-mhapa aig bonn na sgrìn no leis an iuchair “m” air a’ mheur-chlàr."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:222
msgid ""
"The minimap shows the complete map in miniature. You can directly jump to "
"any field by left-clicking on it. You can also toggle buildings, roads, "
"flags and player indicators on and off inside the minimap."
msgstr "Seallaidh am meanbh-mhapa am mapa slàn dhut ann an uinneag bheag. ’S urrainn dhut leum a ghearradh gu raon sam bith ’s tu a’ briogadh air leis a’ phutan chlì. ’S urrainn dhut togalaichean, rathaidean, brataich is taisbeanairean nan chluicheadairean am broinn a’ mheanbh-mhapa a thoglachadh cuideachd."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:224
msgid ""
"Try it out. Open the minimap, click on a few buttons and try moving around. "
"Close it when you have experimented enough."
msgstr "Siuthad is feuch e. Fosgail am meanbh-mhapa, briog air putan no dhà agus feuch gluasad mu thimcheall. Dùin e nuair a bhios tu air do leòr fheuchainn."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:228
msgid "Learn to use the minimap"
msgstr "Ionnsaich mar a chleachdas tu am meanbh-mhapa"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:231
msgid ""
"Open the minimap by using the third button from the left on the bottom of "
"your screen or the ‘m’ key."
msgstr "Fosgail am mean-mhapa ‘s tu a’ briogadh air an treas putan on aobh chlì aig bonn na sgrìn no a’ brùthadh air an iuchair “m” air a’ mheur-chlàr."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:232
msgid "Play around a bit with the different overlays (roads, flags, etc.)"
msgstr "Feuch na tar-chòmhdachaidhean a tha ann (rathaidean, brataichean is mar sin air adhart)"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:233
msgid ""
"Close the minimap when you are ready to continue by using the same button or"
" ‘m’ again. Of course, a right-click also works."
msgstr "Dùin am meanbh-mhapa nuair a bhios tu deiseil gus leantainn air adhart. Cleachd an t-aon phutan a-rithist no “m” gus seo a dhèanamh. Gu nàdarra, obraichidh briogadh deas cuideachd."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:238
msgid "Onward to the Quarry"
msgstr "Air adhart dhan choireall"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:239
msgid "Great. Now about that quarry…"
msgstr "Taghta. Nise, mu dhèidhinn a’ choirill ud…"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:247
msgid "How to Build a Quarry"
msgstr "Mar a thogas tu coireall"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:249
msgid ""
"Build a quarry next to those rocks here. Remember how I did it earlier?"
msgstr "Tog coireall faisg air na creagan an-seo. A bheil chuimhne agad air mar a rinn mi seo roimhe?"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:250
msgid ""
"Make sure that you are showing the building spaces, then just click on the "
"space were you want the building to be, choose it from the window that "
"appears, and it is placed. Maybe this is a good time to explain about all "
"those building space symbols we activated earlier."
msgstr "Dèan cinnteach gun do nochd thu na h-ionadan togail is an uairsin briog air an àite far a bheil thu airson an togalach a chur ann, tagh on uinneag a nochdas e is thèid a chur ann. Dh’fhaoidte gur e deagh àm a th’ ann gus mìneachadh mu na samhlaidhean ionad togail a ghnìomhaich sinn roimhe."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:251
msgid ""
"You can build four things on fields in Widelands: flags, small houses, "
"medium houses and big houses. But not every field can hold everything. The "
"build space symbols ease recognition:"
msgstr "Tha ceithir rudan as urrainn dhut togail air raointean Widelands: brataich, togalaichean beaga, togalaichean meadhanach is togalaichean mòra. Ach chan eil rum anns gach raon airson gach seòrsa dhiubh. Cuidichidh na samhlaidhean togail ach an aithnich thu na raointean:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:253
msgid "Everything can be built on the green house symbol."
msgstr "Gabhaidh rud sam bith a thogail air samhla taighe uaine."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:254
msgid ""
"Everything except for big buildings can be built on a yellow house symbol."
msgstr "Gabhaidh rud sam bith ach togalaichean mòra a thogail air samhla taighe buidhe."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:255
msgid "Red building symbols can only hold small buildings and flags."
msgstr "Chan urrainn dhut ach togalach beag no bratach a thogail air samhla taighe dearg."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:256
msgid "And finally, the yellow flag symbol only allows for flags."
msgstr "Cha cheadaich samhla brataich buidhe ach gun tog thu bratach ann."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:258
msgid ""
"If you place something on a field, the surrounding fields might have less "
"space for holding buildings, so choose your fields wisely."
msgstr "Ma thogas tu rudeigin air raon, dh’fhaoidte nach bi an aon uiread de rum aig na raointean timcheall air tuilleadh gus togalaichean a chur ann. Mar sin, bi glic mu thaghadh nan raointean agad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:260
msgid ""
"Now go ahead, try it. The quarry is a small building, so if you click on a "
"medium or big building symbol, you will have to select the small buildings "
"tab first to find it. Go on, check it out!"
msgstr "Siuthad is feuch e a-nis. ’S e togalach beag a th’ anns a’ choireall, mar sin ma bhriogas tu air samhla togail meadhanach no mòr, feumaidh tu taba nan togalaichean beaga a thaghadh an toiseach gus a lorg. Siuthad, thoir sùil air!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:263
msgid "Build a quarry next to the rocks"
msgstr "Tog coireall ri taobh nan creagan"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:265
msgid "Build a Quarry"
msgstr "Tog coireall"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:267
msgid ""
"There are some rocks to the west of your headquarters. Build a quarry right "
"next to them."
msgstr "Tha creagan gu siar air a’ phrìomh-àras agad. Tog coireall ris an taobh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:268
msgid ""
"The quarry is a small building like the lumberjack’s hut. You can therefore "
"build it on any field that shows a red, yellow or green house when the "
"building spaces symbols are enabled (Press SPACE for that)."
msgstr "’S e togalach beag a tha sa choireall mar a tha am bothan coillteir. Mar sin, ’s urrainn dhut fear a thogail air raon sam bith a sheallas taigh dearg, buidhe no uaine nuair a bhios na h-ionadan togail ’gan nochdadh (brùth air SPACE gus an nochdadh)."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:269
msgid ""
"Just click on any house symbol next to the rocks, select the small buildings"
" tab in the window that opens up, then click on the quarry symbol."
msgstr "Briog air samhla taighe sam bith ri taobh nan creagan, tagh taba nan togalaichean beaga san uinneag a nochdas is an uairsin briog air samhla a’ choirill."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:276
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:293
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:310
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:318
msgid "Road Building"
msgstr "A’ togail rathad"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:278
msgid ""
"Excellent! Directly after placing the building, you have been switched into "
"road building mode. The new road will start at the flag in front of your "
"newly placed construction site. You can enter road building mode for any "
"flag by left-clicking on a flag and selecting"
msgstr "Taghta! Nuair a bhios tu air togalach a chur ann, bidh thu sa mhodh togail rathaidean. Tòisichidh an rathad ùr aig a’ bhratach air beulaibh na làraich-togail ùir agad. ’S urrainn dhut tionndadh dhan mhodh togail rathaidean airson brataich sam bith ’s tu a’ briogadh leis a’ phutan clì air a’ bhratach is a’ taghadh"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:280
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:297
msgid "the road building symbol."
msgstr "an t-samhla “Tog rathaidean”."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:282
msgid ""
"If you decide you do not want to build a road at this time, you can cancel "
"road building by clicking on the starting flag of the road and selecting"
msgstr "Ma chuireas tu romhad nach tog thu rathad an-dràsta, ’s urrainn dhut sgur de thogail an rathaid ’s tu a’ briogadh air bratach tòiseachaidh an rathaid ’s a’ taghadh"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:283
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:300
msgid "the abort symbol."
msgstr "an t-samhla “Sguir dheth”."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:285
msgid ""
"Now, about this road. Remember: we are already in road building mode since "
"you just ordered the quarry. You can either make it longer by one field at a"
" time by left-clicking multiple times on neighboring fields for perfect "
"control over the route the road takes, like so:"
msgstr "Nise, tòisicheamaid air an rathad. Cuimhnich gu bheil sinn ann am modh togail rathaidean mar-thà on a tha thu air coireall òrdachadh. ’S urrainn dhut an rathad a dhèanamh nas fhaide raon air raon ’s tu a’ briogadh iomadh turas air raointean nàbaidh airson smachd mhionaidich air far an tèid an rathad. Seallaidh mi seo dhut a-nis:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:295
msgid ""
"Excellent! To enter road building mode for any flag, left-click on a flag "
"and select"
msgstr "Sgoinneil! Gus dol a-steach dhan mhodh togail rathaidean airson bratach sam bith, dèan briogadh clì air a’ bhratach agus tagh"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:299
msgid ""
"If you decide that you do not want to build a road at this time, you can "
"cancel road building by clicking on the starting flag of the road and "
"selecting"
msgstr "Ma chuireas tu romhad nach tog thu rathad an-dràsta, ’s urrainn dhut sgur de thogail an rathaid ’s tu a’ briogadh air bratach tòiseachaidh an rathaid ’s a’ taghadh"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:302
msgid ""
"Now, about this road. I’ll enter the road building mode and then make it "
"longer by one field at a time by left-clicking multiple times on neighboring"
" fields for perfect control over the route the road takes, like so:"
msgstr "Nise, tòisicheamaid air an rathad. thèid mi a-steach dhan mhodh togail rathaidean agus nì mi an rathad nas fhaide raon air raon ’s mi a’ briogadh iomadh turas air raointean nàbaidh airson smachd mhionaidich air far an tèid an rathad. Seallaidh mi seo dhut a-nis:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:311
msgid ""
"Or, you can directly click the flag where the road should end, like so:"
msgstr "No briog dìreach air a’ bhratach far am bu chòir an rathad a chrìochnachadh mar a nì mi a-nis:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:320
msgid ""
"One more thing: around the field where your road would end, you can see "
"different markers. They have the following meaning:"
msgstr "Aon rud eile: chì thu caochladh de chomharran mun raon far an crìochnaicheadh an rathad agad. Seo nas ciall dhaibh:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:322
msgid ""
"The terrain is flat here. Your carriers will be very swift on this terrain."
msgstr "Tha an tìr rèidh an-seo. Bidh na giùlanairean glè luath air."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:323
msgid ""
"There is a small slope to climb to reach this field. This means that your "
"workers will be faster walking downhill than they will be walking uphill."
msgstr "Tha sliabh bheag ri dìreadh ann gus an raon seo a ruigsinn. Is ciall dha seo gun gluais na h-obraichean agad nas luaithe a’ teàrnadh na a’ dìreadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:324
msgid ""
"The connection between the fields is extremely steep. The speed increase in "
"one direction is huge while the slowdown in the other is also substantial."
msgstr "Tha an ceangal eadar an dà raon uabhasach cas. Buannaichidh tu luaths mòr air an dàrna comhair ach thèid maille mhòr a chur ort air a’ chomhair eile cuideachd."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:326
msgid ""
"Keep the slopes in mind while placing roads and use them to your advantage. "
"Also, try to keep roads as short as possible and always remember to place as"
" many flags as you can on road segments to share the load better. If you "
"hold Ctrl or Shift+Ctrl while you finish the road, flags are placed "
"automatically."
msgstr "Thoir an aire air na slèibhtean nuair a thogas tu rathaidean is faigh buannachd asta. Feuch cuideachd gun cum thu na rathaidean cho goirid ’s a ghabhas is cuimhnich gun tog thu an uiread de bhrataich a ghabhas air roinnean an rathaid gus an eallach a sgaoileadh nas fhearr. Ma chumas tu Ctrl no Shift+Ctrl sìos fad ’s a bhios tu a’ cur crìoch air an rathad, thèid na brataich a chur ann gu fèin-obrachail."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:328
msgid "Now please rebuild the road between your quarry and your headquarters."
msgstr "An tog thu an rathad eadar an coireall agus am prìomh-àras agad as ùr?"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:332
msgid "Connect the quarry to the headquarters"
msgstr "Ceangail an coireall ris a’ phrìomh-àras"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:334
msgid "Connect Your Construction Site"
msgstr "Ceangail an làrach togail agad"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:335
msgid ""
"Connect your quarry construction site to your headquarters with a road. You "
"would have been put directly into road building mode after ordering a new "
"site. But now, you aren’t."
msgstr "Ceangal làrach togail a’ choirill ris a’ phrìomh-àras agad le rathad. Bhiodh thu ann am modh togail rathaidean sa bhad nan robh thu dìreach air làrach ùr òrdachadh. Ach chan eil thu an-dràsta."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:337
msgid ""
"To build a completely new road, just click on the flag in front of your "
"construction site, click on the build road icon and then click on the flag "
"in front of your headquarters. Wait for the completion of the quarry."
msgstr "Gus rathad ùr a thogail, cha leig thu leas ach briogadh air a’ bhratach air beulaibh an làraich togail agad is an uairsin air an ìomhaigheag togail rathaid is air a’ bhratach air beulaibh a’ phrìomh-àrais agad. Fuirich ort an uairsin gus am bi an coireall deiseil."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:342
msgid "Quarry not Connected"
msgstr "Cha deach an coireall a cheangal"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:344
msgid ""
"Your workers do not like to walk across country. You have to build a road "
"from your headquarters to the construction site so that carriers can "
"transport wares. The simplest way is to click on the construction site’s "
"flag, choose ‘Build road’, and then click on the destination flag (the one "
"in front of your headquarters), just like I’ve demonstrated."
msgstr "Cha toil leis na h-obraichean agad coiseachd a’ bhlàir. Feumaidh tu rathad a thogail on phrìomh-àras agad dhan làrach togail ach an urrainn dha na giùlanairean bathar a thogail dha. Seo ann dòigh as fhasa gus rathad a thogail: briog air bratach an làraich thogail, tagh “Tog rathad” is an uairsin briog air bratach a’ chinn-uidhe (seo an tè air beulaibh a’ phrìomh-àrais agad) mar a sheall mi dhut."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:351
msgid "You Destroyed the Construction Site!"
msgstr "Mhill thu an làrach togail!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:353
msgid ""
"It seems like you destroyed a construction site for a quarry we wanted to "
"build. Since we need the stones, I suggest you reload the game from a "
"previous savegame. Luckily, these are created from time to time. To do so, "
"you have to go back to the main menu and choose ‘Single Player’ → ‘Load "
"Game’. And please be a bit more careful next time."
msgstr "Na mhill thu làrach togail a’ choirill a bha sinn airson togail? On a tha sinn feumach air na clachan, mholainn gun luchdaich thu an geama às ùr o gheama air a shàbhaladh. Gu fortanach, cruthaichidh sinn fear dhut o àm gu àm. Gus geama a luchdadh, till dhan phrìomh chlàr-taice agus tagh “Aon chluicheadair” → “Luchdaich geama”. Agus nach bi thu nas fhaiceallaiche an ath thuras?"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:361
msgid "Build a second quarry"
msgstr "Tog coireall eile"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:363
msgid ""
"When there are many rocks, you can consider building another quarry. This "
"will make the stone production faster."
msgstr "Nuair a bhios torr chreagan ann, thoir fainear dhut an tog thu coireall eile. Gheibh thu clachan nas luaithe mar sin."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:365
msgid ""
"Build a second quarry near the rocks and connect it to your road network."
msgstr "Tog coireall eile faisg air na creagan agus ceangail e ri lìonra nan rathaidean agad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:368
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:370
msgid "Build another quarry"
msgstr "Tog coireall eile"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:371
msgid ""
"Build a second quarry next to the rocks. Do not forget to connect it to "
"another flag."
msgstr "Tog coireall eile faisg air na creagan: Na dìochuimhnich a cheangail ri bratach eile."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:373
msgid ""
"You can connect the new road to any flag of your existing road network. You "
"can create junctions everywhere, not only in front of buildings."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut an rathad ùr a cheangal ri bratach sam bith air lìonra nan rathaidean a th’ agad. ’S urrainn dhut goibhlean a chruthachadh àite sam bith seach air beulaibh thogalaichean a-mhàin."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:380
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:389
msgid "Census and Statistics"
msgstr "Cunntas-sluaigh is stadastaireachd"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:382
msgid ""
"While we wait, I’ll quickly show you another useful feature. All "
"construction sites look the same, and some buildings look alike. It is "
"sometimes hard to tell them apart. Widelands offers a feature to show label "
"texts over the buildings. They are called the ‘census’ and you can toggle "
"them via the ‘c’ key or via the button on the ‘Watch’ tab of any field."
msgstr "Fhad ’s a tha sinn a’ feitheamh, seallaidh mi feart feumail eile dhut. Tha an aon choltas aig gach làrach-togail is tha cuid a thogalaichean uabhasach coltach ri chèile. Tha e doirbh aig amannan aithneachadh dè seòrsa togalaich a chì thu. Tairgidh Widelands feart dhut a nochdas ainm os cionn gach togalaich. Chuir sinn “cunntas-sluaigh” air is toglaichidh tu leis an iuchair “c” e no leis a’ phutan air an taba “Cum sùil air” aig raon sam bith."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:383
msgid ""
"Similar to this are the building statistics, which are also toggled via a "
"button on the ‘Watch’ tab of any field. The hotkey for it is ‘s’. This will "
"display information about the productivity of buildings or the progress of "
"construction sites."
msgstr "Tha stadastaireachd nan togalach coltach ri seo is toglaichidh tu i le putan air an taba “Cum sùil air” aig raon sam bith. Is “s” an hotkey air a son. Seallaidh seo fiosrachadh mu shaothrachadh nan togalach is adhartas nan làraichean-togail."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:384
msgid ""
"Let me quickly enable these two for you. Remember: ‘c’ and ‘s’ are the keys."
" Alternatively, you can click on any field without a building on it, select "
"the watch tab and then click on the corresponding buttons."
msgstr "Nach cuir mi an dà dhiubh an comas dhut? Cuir nad chuimhne: Is “c” agus “s” na h-iuchraichean. ’S urrainn dhut cuideachd briogadh air raon sam bith air nach eil togalach, an taba “Cum sùil air” a thaghadh is an uairsin briogadh air na putanan iomchaidh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:390
msgid "Now we know what’s going on. Let’s wait for the quarries to finish."
msgstr "Tha fios againn a-nis air na tha a’ tachairt. Fuirich ort a-nis gus am bi an dà choireall deiseil."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:397
msgid "Introducing Messages"
msgstr "Seo teachdaireachd"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:399
msgid "Messages"
msgstr "Teachdaireachdan"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:400
msgid ""
"Hi, it’s me again! This time, I have sent you a message. Messages are sent "
"to you by Widelands to inform you about important events: empty mines, "
"attacks on your tribe, won or lost military buildings, resources found…"
msgstr "Seo mise a-rithist! Chuir mi teachdaireachd thugad an turas seo. Cuiridh Widelands teachdaireachdan thugad airson innse dhut mu thachartasan cudromach: mèinn fhalamh, ionnsaigh air an treubh agad, togalach an airm a chaill no cheannsaich thu, stòras air a lorg…"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:401
msgid ""
"The message window can be toggled by the button on the very right at the "
"bottom of the screen. This button will also change appearance whenever new "
"messages are available, but there is also a bell sound played whenever you "
"receive a new message."
msgstr "Gabhaidh uinneag nan teachdaireachd a thoglachadh leis a’ phutan as fhaide deas aig a’ bhonn. Barrachd air sin, atharraichidh coltas a’ phutain seo nuair a bhios teachdaireachd ùr ri làimh, ach cluinnidh tu clag cuideachd gach turas a thig teachdaireachd ùr a-steach."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:402
msgid ""
"You have two messages at the moment. This one, which you are currently "
"reading, and the one that informed you that a new headquarters was added to "
"your economy. Let’s learn how to archive messages: You can check them off in"
" your inbox so that they get a tick-symbol in front of them. Then, you can "
"click the"
msgstr "Tha dà theachdaireachd agad an-dràsta. An tè seo a tha thu a’ leughadh an-dràsta is an tè eile a dh’innis dhut gun robh prìomh-àras ùr air a chur ris an eaconamaidh agad. Ionnsaicheamaid mar a chuireas tu teachdaireachd dhan tasglann: ’s urrainn dhut cromag a chur sa bhogsa air a beulaibh. An uairsin, ’s urrainn dhut briogadh air"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:404
msgid "archive message button to move them into your archive."
msgstr "a’ phutan “Cuir na teachdaireachdan a thagh thu san tasglann” gus an cur san tasglann agad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:407
msgid ""
"Archive all messages that you currently have in your inbox, including this "
"one."
msgstr "Cuir na h-uile teachdaireachd sa bhogsa a-steach agad dhan tasglann, a’ gabhail a-steach an tè seo."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:410
msgid "Archive all messages in your inbox"
msgstr "Cuir na h-uile teachdaireachd dhan tasglann"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:412
msgid "Archive Your Inbox Messages"
msgstr "Cuir na teachdaireachdan sa bhogsa a-steach agad dhan tasglann"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:413
msgid ""
"The message window is central to fully controlling your tribe’s fortune. "
"However, you will get a lot of messages in a real game. To keep your head "
"straight, you should try to keep the inbox empty."
msgstr "Tha uinneag nan teachdaireachd cudromach gus fortan na treubha agad a stiùireadh gu slàn. Co-dhiù, gheibh thu torr theachdaireachdan rè geama àbhaistich. Bu choir dhut am bogsa a-steach a chumail glan ach an dèan thu bun no barr dheth."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:415
msgid "Archive all your messages in your inbox now."
msgstr "Cuir na h-uile teachdaireachd agad san tasglann a-nis."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:416
msgid ""
"To do so, open the message window by pressing ‘n’ or clicking the rightmost "
"button at the very bottom of the screen. Then mark all messages by checking "
"the check box in front of them. Then, click the ‘Archive All’ button."
msgstr "An toiseach, fosgail uinneag nan teachdaireachd ’s tu a’ brùthadh air “n” no a’ briogadh air a’ phutan as fhaide deas aig a bhonn. Comharraich na h-uile teachdaireachd an uairsin ’s tu a’ cur cromag sa bhogsa air am beulaibh. An uairsin, briog air a’ phutan “Cuir na teachdaireachdan a thagh thu san tasglann.”"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:423
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:444
msgid "Closing Windows"
msgstr "A’ dùnadh uinneagan"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:425
msgid ""
"Excellent. Do you remember how to close windows? You simply have to right-"
"click on them. This will work with all windows except for story message "
"windows like this one. Go ahead and try it."
msgstr "Taghta. A bheil chuimhne agad air mar a dhùineas tu uinneag? Cha leig thu leas ach briogadh oirre le putan deas na luchaige. Obraichidh seo leis a h-uile uinneag ach uinneagan sgeulachd a leithid an tè seo. Siuthad is feuch e."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:427
msgid ""
"First, close this window by pressing the button below, then right-click into"
" the messages window to close it."
msgstr "Dùin an uinneag seo leis a’ phutan gu h-ìosal an toiseach is dèan briogadh deas air uinneag nan teachdaireachd an uairsin gus a dùnadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:432
msgid "Close the messages window"
msgstr "Dùin uinneag nan teachdaireachd"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:434
msgid "Close the Messages Window"
msgstr "Dùin uinneag nan teachdaireachd"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:435
msgid ""
"All windows in Widelands can be closed by right-clicking into them. Some "
"windows can also be toggled with the buttons at the very bottom of the "
"screen."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut uinneag sam bith ann am Widelands a dhùnadh ’s tu a’ dèanamh briogadh deas air. Gabhaidh cuid a dh’uinneagan a thoglachadh leis na putanan aig bonn na sgrìn cuideachd."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:437
msgid "Close the messages window now by right-clicking into it."
msgstr "Dùin uinneag nan teachdaireachd a-nis ’s tu a’ briogadh air leis a’ phutan deas."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:446
msgid ""
"Well done! Let’s see how messages work in a real game, shall we? For this, "
"I’ll take all rocks away from the poor stonemasons in the quarries. They "
"will then send a message each that they can’t find any in their working "
"areas the next time they try to do some work."
msgstr "Sin thu fhèin! Nise, nach toir sin sùil air mar a dh’obraicheas teachdaireachdan am broinn geama? Bheir mi na h-uile creag air falbh o na clachairean bochda a-nis. Cuiridh gach fear dhiubh teachdaireachd an uairsin nach urrainn dhaibh creagan a lorg san roinn obrach aca tuilleadh an ath thuras a dh’fheuchas iad ri obair a dhèanamh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:454
msgid "Messages Arrived!"
msgstr "Thàinig teachdaireachdan a-steach!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:456
msgid ""
"You received some messages. See how the button at the bottom of the screen "
"has changed appearance? You can destroy the quarries now as they are no "
"longer of any use and just blocking space. To do so, there are two "
"possibilities:"
msgstr "Fhuair thu teachdaireachdan. Am faic thu mar a dh’atharraich dreach a’ phutain taobh deas aig bonn na sgrìn? ’S urrainn dhut cuidhteas fhaighinn dhe na coirill a-nis o nach eil iad gu feum dhut tuilleadh ’s a’ toirt rum uat. Tha dà dhòigh ann gus seo a dhèanamh:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:458
msgid ""
"Burning down the quarry: this is the fastest way of clearing the space. "
"While the worker abandons the building, the wares are lost."
msgstr "Milleadh a’ choirill: seo an dòigh as luaithe gus an rum fhaighinn air ais. Fad ’s a dh’fhalbhas an t-obraiche thèid gach bathair san togalach air chall."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:459
msgid ""
"Dismantling the quarry: a builder will walk from the headquarters to "
"dismantle the quarry piece by piece. Thereby, you regain some of the "
"resources you used for the construction."
msgstr "A’ toirt a’ choirill às a chèile: thig neach-togail on phrìomh-àras gus an coireall a thoirt às a chèile beag air bheag. Le sin, gheibh thu cuid dhe na stòrasan a chleachd thu gus a thogail air ais."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:465
msgid ""
"Since our quarries are useless now, you can destroy them and reuse the space"
" later on."
msgstr "O nach eil na coirill againn gu feum sam bith tuilleadh, ’s urrainn dhut am milleadh agus an rum a chleachdadh a-rithist an uairsin."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:467
msgid ""
"There are two different ways of destroying a building: burning down and "
"dismantling. Try them both out on your quarries."
msgstr "Tha dà dhòigh ann gus cuidhteas fhaighinn de thogalach: mill e no thoir às a chèile e. Feuch an dà chuid dhiubh air an dà choireall agad."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:468
msgid ""
"Burning down the quarry: This is the fastest way of clearing the space. "
"While the worker abandons the building, the wares are lost."
msgstr "Milleadh a’ choirill: seo an dòigh as luaithe gus an rum fhaighinn air ais. Fad ’s a dh’fhalbhas an t-obraiche thèid gach bathair san togalach air chall."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:469
msgid ""
"Dismantling the quarry: A builder will walk from the headquarters to "
"dismantle the quarry piece by piece. Thereby, you regain some of the "
"resources you used for the construction."
msgstr "A’ toirt a’ choirill às a chèile: thig neach-togail on phrìomh-àras gus an coireall a thoirt às a chèile beag air bheag. Le sin, gheibh thu cuid dhe na stòrasan a chleachd thu gus a thogail air ais."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:474
msgid "Expanding Your Territory!"
msgstr "A’ meudachadh na tìre agad!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:476
msgid ""
"There is one more thing I’d like to teach you now: Expanding your territory."
" The place that we started with around our headquarters is barely enough for"
" a basic building infrastructure, and we do not have access to mountains, "
"which we need to mine minerals and coal. So, we have to expand our "
"territory."
msgstr "Tha rud ann a bu toil leam ionnsachadh dhut fhathast: ’s e seo mar a mheudaicheas tu an tìr agad. ’S gann gum foghainn an rum timcheall air a’ phrìomh-àras a thòisich thu leis airson bun-structair togail bhunasaich is cha ruig sinn na beanntan a dh’fheumas sinn airson mhèinnearach is guail. Seo as adhbhar gum feum sinn an roinn a th’ againn a mheudachadh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:477
msgid ""
"Expanding is as simple as building a military building at the edge of your "
"territory. The Barbarians have a selection of different military buildings: "
"sentries, barriers, donjons, fortresses and citadels. The bigger the "
"building, the more expensive it is to build, but the more land it will "
"conquer around itself and the more soldiers can be stationed there. The "
"buildings also vary in their vision range: buildings with a tower see "
"farther than others."
msgstr "Tha meudachadh na tìre agad cho simplidh ri togail togalach an airm air crìochan do dhùthcha. Tha roghainn de thogalaichean an airm aig na Tùsanaich: freiceadain, taighean-faire, tùir-fhaire is cathraichean. Mar as motha an togalach ’s ann as cosgaile a bhios e, ’s ann as motha an tìr a cheannsaicheas e is ’s ann as motha an àireamh de shaighdearan a ghabhas còmhnaidh ann. Tha astar lèirsinne eadar-dhealaichte aig gach togalach cuideachd: chì togalaichean aig a bheil tùr nas fhaide na càch."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:478
msgid ""
"As soon as a military building is manned, it will extend your land. I will "
"tell your more about military buildings in another tutorial."
msgstr "Cho luath ’s a bhios saighdear air còmhnaidh a ghabhail ann an togalach an airm agad, meudaichidh do ranntair. Innsidh mi barrachd dhut mu thogalaichean an airm ann an oideachadh eile."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:480
msgid "Let’s try it out now: build a military building on your border."
msgstr "Feuchamaid ris an-dràsta: tog togalach an airm aig a’ chrìoch."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:481
msgid ""
"The sentry is the only military site that fits on a small building plot. If "
"your lumberjack has cleared enough space, you can also build another "
"military building."
msgstr "’S e am freiceadan a tha san aon togalach an airm as urrainn dhut togail air raon-togail beag. Ma tha an coilltear agad air rum gu leòr a chruthachadh, ’s urrainn dhut togalaichean an airm eile a thogail cuideachd a tha nas motha."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:484
msgid "Expand your territory"
msgstr "A’ meudachadh na tìre agad"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:486
msgid "Make your territory grow"
msgstr "Meudaich do ranntair"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:487
msgid ""
"In Widelands, it is necessary to build many buildings, which take up a lot "
"of space. To expand your territory, you have to build military buildings "
"next to your border. Every tribe has several military buildings."
msgstr "Ann am Widelands, feumaidh gu iomadh togalach a thogail agus bidh feum aca air torr ruim. Gus do ranntair a mheudachadh, feumaidh tu togalaichean an airm a thogail faisg air na crìochan agad. Tha taghadh dhe thogalaichean an airm aig gach treubh."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:489
msgid ""
"The Barbarians have four different military buildings you can build: the "
"sentry (small), the barrier and the donjon (both medium) and the fortress "
"(big). Just choose the one you like most."
msgstr "Tha ceithir togalaichean an airm aig na tùsanaich as urrainn dhut togail: am freiceadan (beag), an taigh-faire agus an tùr-faire (meadhanach an dà chuid dhiubh) agus an dùn (mòr). Tagh am fear as fhearr leat."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:490
msgid ""
"Remember that big buildings (green icon) cannot be built on small (red) or "
"medium (yellow) building plots, but buildings can be built on a building "
"plot that provides more space than they need. You should always keep that in"
" mind when you search for a suitable place."
msgstr "Cuimhnich nach gabh togalaichean mòra (ìomhaigheag uaine) a thogail air raointean-togail meadhanach (buidhe) no beaga (dearga) ach gabhaidh togalaichean a thogail air raon a gheibh barrachd ruim dhaibh na tha feum aca air. Bu chòir dhut seo a chumail ’nad aire an-còmhnaidh nuair a bhios tu a’ sireadh àite freagarrach."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:496
msgid "Military Site Occupied"
msgstr "Ghabh na saighdearan agad còmhnaidh ann an togalach an airm"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:498
msgid "Your territory has just grown!"
msgstr "Tha do ranntair air a mheudachadh!"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:499
msgid ""
"Great. Do you see how your territory has grown since your soldiers entered "
"your new military building?"
msgstr "Taghta. Am faca thu mar a mheudaich do ranntair on a chaidh na saighdearan agad a-steach dha thogalach an airm ùr agad?"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:500
msgid ""
"Every military building has a certain conquer area – the more expensive the "
"building, the more land it conquers."
msgstr "Tha astar ceannsachaidh aig gach togalach an airm – mar as cosgaile an togalach ’s ann as motha de thìr a cheannsaicheas e."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:507
#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:509
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "Co-dhùnadh"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:510
msgid ""
"This concludes the first tutorial. In order to learn more about the game, I "
"suggest to play one of the other tutorials. Each of them covers a different "
"topic."
msgstr "Seo deireadh a’ chiad oideachaidh. Mholainn gun cluich thu fear dhe na cnàmh-sgeulan oideachaidh eile ach an ionnsaich thu barrachd mun gheama. Mìnichidh gach fear dhiubh cuspair eadar-dhealaichte dhut."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:511
msgid ""
"However, since you now know how to control Widelands, you can also start a "
"game (or continue this one) and discover more by yourself."
msgstr "Co-dhiù no co-dheth, on a tha thu eòlach air innealan-stiùiridh Widelands a-nis, ’s urrainn dhut geama a thòiseachadh cuideachd (no leantainn air adhart leis an fhear seo) agus barrachd fhaighinn a-mach air do cheann fhèin."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:512
msgid "To leave this game and return to the main menu, click on the"
msgstr "Gus an geama seo fhàgail agus tilleadh dhan phrìomh chlàr-taice, briog air"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:514
msgid ""
"‘Options’ menu button on the very left at the bottom of the screen. Then "
"click the"
msgstr "a’ phutan clàr-taice “Roghainnean” taobh clì aig bonn na sgrìn. An uairsin, briog air"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:515
msgid "‘Exit Game’ button."
msgstr "a’ phutan “Fàg an geama”."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01_basic_control.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:516
msgid ""
"Thanks for playing this tutorial. Enjoy Widelands and remember to visit us "
"at"
msgstr "Mòran taing airson an t-oideachadh seo a chluiche. Gabh tlachd à Widelands is tadhail oirnn air"

